{"tid":1467434,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"得啦，知我地輸左啦","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:18:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:47:52.000Z","uid":122031,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c2e771e686ab4fbaa169d60a654060b469a59d00","tid":1467434,"uid":122031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:18:18.000Z","msg":"輸你老味咩輸 個個上熱門既po都係話我地輸左 又唔撚比提議可以點做下一步既行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n 我地仲未輸！無野可以輸！"},{"pid":"7b9baf953f1eafa8eef92a8ad560f9d4f7154a02","tid":1467434,"uid":5205,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:22:16.000Z","msg":"必須保護100%和理非行動 <br />\n<br />\n我地可以提早決定100%和理非定 有後續 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警察風向 破壞連登 咩淪陷 唔好信<br />\n<br />\n信左就中警察計<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n和理非 取消黑衫行動 勇武就無左保護 鬼亦無咁多機會滲透<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一定要支持 勇武就無左保護 自然要勇武休息下<br />\n咁鬼既滲透亦無左機會。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係 講到明有下場既就全民黑衫 （例如免費過海之類）<br />\n<br />\n機場只宣傳 同控制人流 有人搞事就 比泛民 等泛民開記者會<br />\n<br />\n幫手講佢係鬼 <br />\n<br />\n另外唔建議帶口罩 和理非活動係要一家大細都可以參與"},{"pid":"ade271afa643a02d05f254c06ee48768e59a2a6a","tid":1467434,"uid":122031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:23:28.000Z","msg":"8.18遊行"},{"pid":"a67061870404c4413393c382d91e245b38dfb2c9","tid":1467434,"uid":299733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:24:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcd1034247f09b9ce30b945f7b8fe735ed798b2e","tid":1467434,"uid":111694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:24:31.000Z","msg":"［中計撚入］唔好成日話輸民心啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466381\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466381</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c71cc0ab1a19b192095ffbf56488cd89e8b8bc8e","tid":1467434,"uid":122031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:44:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},